Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is oliver queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,After five years in hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come home\Nwith only one goal--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To save my city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now others have\Njoined my crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To them, I am oliver queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But to the rest\Nof starling city,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Previously, on "arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My name\Nis amanda waller,\Nmr. Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome\Nto hong kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanda waller\Nwants you working for her.\NShe will have her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're felicity smoak.\NI know a guy who might
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Be interested\Nin hiring someone\Nwith your expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently there's another\Nbidder for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?\NRay palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ndoing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicity,\Nall I'm trying to do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is make things\Neasier on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,By having me\Ncompletely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconfigure\Nour phone system?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even know\Nhow difficult it is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To ping a clone\Noff a hacked\Ntransband multiplex?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but only because\Nyou weren't speaking\Nenglish just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know\Nwhere else\Nto take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicity: Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god! Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't\Nleave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicity: We have to--\Ncall--we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her\Nto the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ollie. Ollie,\Nit's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We just got her\Nback, it's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take\Nour position here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your target?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a target--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Might have escaped\Nyour notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But amanda waller\Ndoesn't have a sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why'd she drag\Nme off of lian yu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And bring me all\Nthe way to hong kong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To become her hit man?\NTo become her operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously she needs you\Nfor something or she wouldn't\Nbe threatening my family
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To assure your compliance.\NThe target will be entering\Nour line any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The target will walk 10 paces\Nthrough the roof garden
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And arrive at his hotel suite.\NThat's your window.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, sara used\Nto have a stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was this old,\Nworn out shark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That she got\Nfrom the starling aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time something awful\Nwould happen to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I would always\Nfind her holding\Nthat stupid little shark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that my sister's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Again the only thing\Nthat I can think about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is finding that dumb\Nstuffed animal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And putting it in her arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing\Nto apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whoever\Ndid this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going\Nto find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When I thought that sara\Ndied on "the gambit,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing\Nthat I could do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Was scream at the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I had so much anger and rage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't know\Nwhat to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going\Nto help you catch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever it is that did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You told us\Nwhere to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just supposed\Nto sit here and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Now you take\Ncare of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is\Ngoing to need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling him now,\Nit would kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now if we wait until\Nwe catch whoever did this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be easier on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know\Nanything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know that\Na bar is the last\Nplace I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[dialing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thea: You've reached thea.\NLeave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thea, it's oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're still\Ntraveling,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just,\NI could really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like\Nto hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So please call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd we get off\Nthe cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Place is\Na drug haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all\Neither been\Ndisabled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or paint-balled\Nby local dealers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where it\Nhappened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[horns honking in distance]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicity told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer stood there,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Loose gravel\Non the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver...\NSara was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Scuff marks\Nback to the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do this\Nright now, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing\Nthat I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I get it.\NMilitary training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay on task.\NYour friend gets shot,\Nyou just keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But oliver...\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm here\Nfor you just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, sara was\Nmy friend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you think\Nyou're going after\Nthe person who did this solo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't possibly\Nbe more wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[cell phone vibrating]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective lance called,\Nhe says it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think\Nhe knows about sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[voice disguised]\Nwhat is it, detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You ok? You look\Nlike someone peed\Nin your cornflakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Another archer\Nin town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dropping bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seen this guy's\Nwork before?\NI might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where\Nscpd's finest\Nmight find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the victim?\NJohn burke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Some corporate\Nfinancier\Nfrom qurac.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like\Nhe wandered into\Nthe wrong part of town
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight looking\Nfor a little local\N"entertainment."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He ended up\Nwith an arrow\Nto the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch your back,\Nall right? Whoever\Nthis guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands are so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I never noticed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always so strong\Nand brave. [sniffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I always envisioned her\Nas this sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazonian warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I could\Nnever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[cell phone vibrates]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. I know I was\Nsupposed to come\Ninto work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I--the--I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a death\Nin the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You have any idea\Nwhat other archer\Ncould have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]\Nthere aren't\Nthat many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe 10 that I know of,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of them are in\Nthe league of assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver,\Nyou don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't\Ntarget their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you find out?\NHe hit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,An abandoned warehouse\Non the corner of\Nthird and lemire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninth floor. The victim\Nwas a construction\Nforeman, tim kauffman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Security cameras\Ncan't get an angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?\NJust some low level dealers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That set up shop\Nin abandoned warehouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like\Nmuch of an archer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be a witness.\NDiggle: Where do you want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Will lyla give you access\Nto a.R.G.U.S.'s database?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To find out who did\Nthis, lyla will give us\Naccess to a.R.G.U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a list of everyone\Non their radar--assassins\Nand mercenaries who use a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thea hasn't\Ncalled back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't\Neliminate the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a target,\Nthat's my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I pointing a gun\Nat my best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this\Nsome sort of test?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. One you failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Flunk me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's a coincidence\Nyour friend just happened
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To show up in hong kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here looking for you!\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When you logged into your email,\Nit set off an account alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead men don't check\Ntheir email, oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is\Nmy fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Waller needs you.\NShe can't let you\Nbe compromised
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By some rich kid flashing\Nyour picture all over hong kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you're the one\Nwho pulls the trigger or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants tommy merlyn\Noff the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a cobalt\Nencrypted workstation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not be\Nusing it to tweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was--I was,\Num, actually just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Accessing an fbi database?\NWhat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Roy, why are you\Nlooking for thea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't\Nthink she is where\Nshe says she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Roy, oliver needs to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This is my fault.\NHe's going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she's in trouble?\NWhat if she's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she just\Nneeds space?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's had five months
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And thousands\Nof miles of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver needs to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to show it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[cell phone vibrates]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What--where\Nare you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone\NI need to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[elevator dings]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it to make a point?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I get it.\NLoud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You are rich.\NYou are impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And frankly, you are\Nthe creepiest form of stalker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That I have ever\Nhad to deal with,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And believe me when\NI'm telling you that\Nthat is saying a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And--what are you doing\Nto our old offices?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You like it? Yeah,\NI'm just trying
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To liven up\Nthe place a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hosting\Nan event tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A pledge drive of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Got to make\Nan impression, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop.\NYou can stop\Nsending me flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can stop\Ntexting me\Nand calling me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And emailing me,\Nbecause I spam\Nthem, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is "spam" a verb now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I am never,\Never, ever going\Nto work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you already do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because you\Nbought the store\Nthat I work at!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.\NYes, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My boss just called\Nand told me that you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's wrong--kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought the holding company\Nwhich owns and operates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All 20,000 tech village stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess either way,\Nyes, I am your boss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can either\Nwork for me here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In a big office\Nwith a big salary,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...You can work\Nfor me there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In that awful uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...I can quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is what\NI just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs] you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Most girls would be\Nflattered that I spent\N$1.2 billion to hire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I do have\Na fairly genius plan\Nfor revamping the stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In case you haven't noticed,\NI am not most girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't\Nneed this. Or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Or any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicity, I--I piss people\Noff on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of business,\Nand, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the smartest guy\Nin any given room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I own that. So I have\Nenough experience with\Npeople being angry with me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To know when\Nthey're really angry\Nat something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You right now are not\Nangry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[inhales, exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, money won't\Nfix this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Money won't solve\Nmost problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the ones that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But talking helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we barely\Nknow each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going\Nto leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, whatever\Nhappened, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It helps to remember that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[elevator dings]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[both grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone was murdered here.\NTell me what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There was\Na black face mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a--like\Na hockey mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please, man--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Diggle, are you\Nat a.R.G.U.S.?\NI've got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a list of archers\N20-long, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How many of them\Nwear masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Simon lacroix.\NMercenary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Goes by "komodo."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Send felicity\Neverything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver, I'm opening up\Nthe file now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel: Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Simon lacroix. Born in\Nsaint-sophie, quebec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Raised by a single mom.\NTerrible credit score.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and wanted\Nfor murder\Nin seven countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I need his location.\NOne minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Put him on speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, indexing all active\Nburner cell phones\Nwithin the city limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be\N10,000 phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but how many\Nare making calls\Nto dear old mom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In saint-sophie, quebec?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him.\NHe's on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires squealing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I found lacroix.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to see\Nwhat's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Blowing up\Nstreet camera feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[motor revving]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires squealing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up.\NOliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[sirens]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[revving engine]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I had him, diggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you look,\Nhe almost had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out canvassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about\Nthe driver of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is erlich\Nkelso. He just got out\Nof starling general--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And where are we\Nwith lacroix?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He ditched\Nhis burner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm searching the city\Nfor any calls made to quebec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We used that to track\Nhim once; he's not going\Nto let it happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so why\Ndon't we stop\Nsearching for lacroix
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And start searching\Nfor his target?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there\Nmust be a connection\Nwith his victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Already on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what if we just--\Nwe go to a local morgue
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And we find a body\Nthat looks like tommy's?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At the hong kong morgue?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a better chance\Nof winning the lottery
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And trying to pay waller off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not going\Nto assassinate\Nmy best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?\NThere has to be\Nanother way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it involves\Namanda waller
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding someone else\Nto execute your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not you, dad.\NLook, I'm already\Nin hong kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No, I didn't tell you\NI was taking the jet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I knew you would\Nfreak out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know\Nhow long, ok?\NIt doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, if oliver\Nis still alive,\Nif he is still here--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, why don't you just\Ngo back to banging\Nyour pilates instructor, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:20:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just\Nbe here searching\Nfor my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, miss.\NYou can't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel lance.\NI'm with the district\Nattorney's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Erlich kelso\Nis a witness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of my ongoing\Ninvestigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kelso's under\Nprotective custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not from me.\NAnd if you have\Na problem with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call\Nyour captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him his\Ndaughter says hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I work in the da's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I already\Ntold the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nanything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have to ask you\Na few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't\Nthis working?\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's running an nsa\Nalgorithm aggregating
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The victims' personal\Ninformation using
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Every government database\Nknown, and unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's taking too\Nlong. Sara's killer\Nis still out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that\Nevery minute that\Nwe waste down here--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! You don't\Nneed to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I don't already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I apologize.\NI just need your a game\Nright now, felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend--our friend--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was shot with arrows\Nand fell off of a rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Her body is upstairs\Nright above us in a freezer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we don't know\Nwhat to do with it--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So I am so sorry, oliver,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have feelings, but maybe\Nif you did, too, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That was mean.\NBut this is sara\Nwe're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you stand there\Nbeing so cold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And rational?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause I don't\Nhave the luxury\Nof falling to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's looking to me\Nto handle things,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To make the right\Ndecisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone\Nis looking to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I grieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody else gets to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still\Na human being, oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're allowed to have feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know sometimes\Nthat it's easier
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To live under that hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier today,\NI was looking at sara,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One of these days\Nit's going to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And this...[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This life that\NI've chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It only ends one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just going\Nto spend your life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiding down here\Nin this cave,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting to die?\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going\Nto wait with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if there's\None thing that\Ntoday has taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that life is precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:23:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want so much more\Nin mine than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start\Nwith the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would someone\Nwant to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing,\Nit's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kelso, despite\Nwhat you may have heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Homicides at the hands\Nof a stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are incredibly rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine how rare homicides\Nby bow and arrow are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the guy\Nwas a sicko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the victim here.\NYou're also a witness--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My witness. And you better\Ngive me something useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you're going to be\Nfacing an obstruction charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think I want\Nto talk to your boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't\Ntreat people like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really, you want\Nto talk to my boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh!\NHow's your arm feeling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,John burke and tim kaufman,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They were also shot by\Nwith arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're too dead\Nto tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh!\NBurke and kaufman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do the two of them\Nhave to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all\Nworking on a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody\Nwas supposed\Nto know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh! Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To build\Nan oil pipe line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For amertek. It's--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.41,0:24:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thea: You've reached thea.\NLeave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.58,0:24:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, thea, it's me. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.45,0:24:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And...I don't know\Nif you're getting\Nthese messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.35,0:24:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would really\Nlike to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.49,0:24:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.99,0:24:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.56,0:24:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.43,0:25:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyla has multiple\Nteams trying to get\Nan angle on lacroix.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.60,0:25:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]\Nwhere's felicity?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.20,0:25:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.00,0:25:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She needed some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.54,0:25:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you\Nneed, oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.84,0:25:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need thea\Nto call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.95,0:25:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going\Nto happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.22,0:25:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.14,0:25:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was during the siege.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.61,0:25:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going\Nto run away together,\Nbut I couldn't leave
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.11,0:25:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Without helping you fight.\NAnd when I came back,\Nshe was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.21,0:25:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything\Nbecause this is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.22,0:25:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew I was lying\Nto her the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.85,0:26:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't\Nsay anything about\Nthe letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.06,0:26:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that\NI should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.76,0:26:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicity, I really\Nneed to talk to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.61,0:26:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, can you...\NCall me back as soon\Nas you get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.98,0:26:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel! Baby,\Nare you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.85,0:26:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.65,0:26:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby, a guy just\Ngot skewered right\Nin front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.68,0:26:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope\Nyou're not fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.09,0:26:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And what the hell\Nwere you doing here\Nin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.12,0:26:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The district attorney's office--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.22,0:26:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did not send you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.49,0:26:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied to my officers\Nand now what,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.89,0:26:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just going\Nto stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.93,0:26:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going\Nto lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.20,0:26:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to talk to him.\NIt was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, sweetie,\NI know you want\Nto help,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.44,0:26:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't\Nneed to take\Nthese kind of risks,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.97,0:26:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?\NPretty sure\Nyour sister's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.97,0:26:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that covered\Nfor the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.51,0:26:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.01,0:27:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.\NWe got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.35,0:27:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.32,0:27:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[cell phone vibrates]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.22,0:27:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something.\NMeet me at verdant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.42,0:27:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Amertek industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.63,0:27:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an oil company\Nbased in starling city.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.66,0:27:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Now that\NI've consolidated
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.23,0:27:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All of lacroix's\Nvictim's records,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.43,0:27:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can run\Nthe algorithm,\Nscan the data
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.23,0:27:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And see who received\Nmoney from amertek.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.80,0:27:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does that take?\NNot long.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.00,0:27:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Three to kelso,\None more to burke,\Ntwo more to kaufman.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.21,0:27:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All from a subsidiary\Nfrom amertek in qurac,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.67,0:27:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Which just happens to be\Nthe largest untapped\Noil field on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.44,0:27:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Looks like\Namertek was trying\Nto strike an oil deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.38,0:27:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And some paid lacroix\Nto stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.71,0:27:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this explains\Nhow sara was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.28,0:27:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara once told me\Nshe worked in qurac.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.62,0:27:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And by "worked,"\NI mean she killed\Npeople for the league.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.59,0:27:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying she might\Nhave brought her work\Nhome with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.99,0:27:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who authorized the payments?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.66,0:27:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A board member of amertek\Ncalled tom westin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.49,0:27:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lacroix's\Nnext target.\NWhat's his location?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.80,0:27:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not believe\Nwhere he's headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.30,0:27:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.10,0:27:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think\Nyou're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.04,0:28:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you.\NAbsolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.71,0:28:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver, the only reason\Nwhy you know where\Nto find him is because--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.64,0:28:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You were reckless.\NAnd lacroix almost\Nput an arrow in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.18,0:28:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.82,0:28:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare tell me\Nto stay put and think\Nthat I'll listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.85,0:28:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know me better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.85,0:28:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara was trained by some\Nof the greatest killers\Nin human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.66,0:28:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacroix put her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.33,0:28:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think\Nhe's going to do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.16,0:28:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about anything\Nexcept for getting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.73,0:28:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will.\NYou couldn't before!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.80,0:28:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him\Nescape again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.68,0:28:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.83,0:28:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.70,0:29:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all\Nfor coming out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.17,0:29:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Given all that has\Nbefallen this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.40,0:29:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy for us to lose hope--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.87,0:29:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To hide in our castles\Nand be thankful that our\Nledges are in the black.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.27,0:29:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we, the city's\Nmost affluent\Nbusinessmen and women
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.41,0:29:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold its future in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.61,0:29:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, I'm making a pledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.15,0:29:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give away\Nhalf of my net worth
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.59,0:29:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To the benefit of our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.66,0:29:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And this will be my salary\Nfor the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.89,0:29:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So tonight, I invite you all\Nto join me in this investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.23,0:29:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just with your money,\Nbut with your ingenuity,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.90,0:29:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And most importantly,\Nyour time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The city is my home,\Nbut it's yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.34,0:29:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So help make star city\Nour future.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.35,0:29:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[all screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.86,0:30:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[both grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.25,0:31:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of the arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.69,0:31:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought\Nyou'd be taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.26,0:31:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.03,0:31:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower your bow and live.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.63,0:31:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We both know\Nthat's not\Ngoing to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.34,0:31:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hired you?!\NWho's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.88,0:31:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want\Nto do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.35,0:31:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.75,0:31:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing him\Nwon't bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.78,0:31:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it won't bring\Nher back, she's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.75,0:31:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have stood where\Nyou are right now;
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.59,0:31:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you're so consumed\Nwith rage you can
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.69,0:31:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly breathe,\Nand you think that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.36,0:31:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking revenge\Nwill make it better,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.10,0:31:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But laurel...It won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.10,0:31:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It only makes it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.03,0:31:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he murdered sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.24,0:31:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.94,0:31:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.34,0:31:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Two nights ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.17,0:31:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You put an arrow in her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.34,0:31:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Two nights ago
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.11,0:32:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was drunk\Nin bludhaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.02,0:32:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying.\NI'm proud of my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.55,0:32:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.62,0:32:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with a gun in your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.72,0:32:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel, you need to stop\Nand listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.22,0:32:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.69,0:32:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he killed my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.39,0:32:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel, sara\Nwouldn't want--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.83,0:32:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.23,0:32:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That this isn't what\Nsara would have wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.53,0:32:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you tell me\Nto think of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.27,0:32:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I am\Nthinking of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.80,0:32:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel, if you pull\Nthat trigger--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.47,0:32:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[clicking]\N[sirens]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.61,0:32:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the bullets\Nout of the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.71,0:32:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.96,0:32:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacroix's alibi\Nchecks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.03,0:32:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Two murders in\Nbludhaven, same mo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.50,0:32:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Same night\Nsara was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.33,0:32:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost killed lacroix.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.27,0:32:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that\Nmatters is you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.94,0:32:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The trail's\Nrun cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.60,0:33:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find\Nwhoever did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.71,0:33:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.91,0:33:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know when.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.48,0:33:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father\Ndeserves to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.75,0:33:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[inhales, exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.46,0:33:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.83,0:33:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance: Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.90,0:33:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some word on the boy.\NYeah, some stuff's come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.37,0:33:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Yeah.\NIt looks pretty good,\Nit looks pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.24,0:33:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacroix, with an "x."\Nyeah. I don't know,\Nthe guy's french
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.27,0:33:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something,\Nwhy you asking--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.51,0:33:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hold on, hold on.\NI got to call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.58,0:33:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel, baby, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.95,0:33:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.16,0:33:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.76,0:33:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me.\NTell me, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.73,0:33:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.26,0:33:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.13,0:34:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.37,0:34:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And you deserve to know\Nthe truth, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.67,0:34:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.71,0:34:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.71,0:34:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn thing\Ngoes off every hour\Nif I don't take my pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.11,0:34:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel, what do you know?\NYou looked like you were
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.62,0:34:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle\Nof telling me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.55,0:34:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted\Nto say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.72,0:34:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.82,0:34:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that I should\Nhave told you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.73,0:34:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.16,0:34:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got to--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.73,0:34:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.37,0:34:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.73,0:34:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.37,0:34:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I always forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.34,0:34:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.17,0:34:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.31,0:34:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She can rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.65,0:34:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.47,0:35:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a jewish custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.87,0:35:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she wasn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.08,0:35:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.12,0:35:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.72,0:36:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.39,0:36:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't--\Nit--she doesn't even\Nget a fresh grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.16,0:36:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so perverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.86,0:36:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She deserves a proper burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.54,0:36:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's earned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.50,0:36:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.07,0:36:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will ever\Nreally know\Nwho she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.81,0:36:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver, it's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.55,0:36:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.90,0:36:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurel, we'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.67,0:36:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this doesn't\Ncount for much,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.10,0:36:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But me and lyla,\Nwe're naming the baby sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.08,0:36:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We will never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.45,0:37:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.28,0:37:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.70,0:37:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.70,0:37:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.04,0:37:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell\Nis going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.00,0:37:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.24,0:37:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.24,0:37:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please don't--\Nplease don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.35,0:37:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just--just\Nlet me go, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.92,0:37:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise, I--I won't\Ntell anybody about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.75,0:37:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Would a fisherman\Nthrow his prized catch\Nback into the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.69,0:37:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs] what\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.52,0:37:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, whoever you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.59,0:37:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't\Nwant to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.10,0:37:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who\NI am? Who my father is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.70,0:37:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thomas merlyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.43,0:37:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been looking\Nfor oliver queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.60,0:37:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How--how do you--\Nhow do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.94,0:38:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A simple hack of a missing\Nbillionaire's email account.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.61,0:38:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew somebody would come\Nlooking for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.71,0:38:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought it would be\Nhis...Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.91,0:38:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His sister.\NBut you, the son
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.29,0:38:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the ceo of merlyn global.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.62,0:38:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.46,0:38:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend,\Nyou are going to make me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.96,0:38:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A very rich man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.66,0:38:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So oliver didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.93,0:38:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.77,0:38:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.37,0:38:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver queen is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.84,0:38:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's rotting\Nat the bottom\Nof the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.51,0:38:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.81,0:38:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If your father doesn't\Npay that ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.58,0:38:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[siren]\NI'm in here,\Nplease help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.62,0:38:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Police! Hong kong police!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.99,0:38:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok.\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.92,0:38:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going home.\NYou're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.11,0:39:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch\Nwhoever killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.55,0:39:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.41,0:39:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And until you do,\NI'm back on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.92,0:39:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What about\Nyour family?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.36,0:39:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara is family,\Noliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.99,0:39:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you,\Nman.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.93,0:39:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.83,0:39:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I got to go get thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.27,0:39:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's long past time\Nshe came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.41,0:39:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,["courage or the fall"\Nby civil twilight playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.01,0:39:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,John.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.32,0:39:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want\Nto die down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.69,0:39:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't, oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.19,0:40:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ man wasn't made\Nto live alone ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.17,0:40:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ that's why I have\Nmy enemies ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.97,0:40:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ whenever I close my eyes ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.42,0:40:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ you're all I can see ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.59,0:40:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ every man needs a savior ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.40,0:40:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ every savior needs his task ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.21,0:40:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ but which one am I ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.61,0:40:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ the man or the one\Nbehind the mask ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.42,0:41:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ what comes first ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.96,0:41:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ courage or the fall ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.00,0:41:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.67,0:41:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.67,0:41:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You changed your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.20,0:41:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just decided I want\Nmore out of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.01,0:41:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[all grunting,\Nhitting sticks]
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.90,0:41:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.68,0:42:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, dad.
